OL,4,Cpound immigration scam from Heathrow'
OL,6,FA former (BA) employee fled to India
OL,7,Fafter he was accused of masterminding
OL,8,Fa multi-million pound immigration scam
OL,9,Ffrom .
OL,11,FPolice arrested a 24-year-old man on
OL,12,FJanuary 6, alleging that he charged
OL,13,Fpeople #25,000 each to help them
OL,14,Fillegally enter Canada from the UK,
OL,15,FThe Times reported.
OL,17,FSo-called "customers" - most of whom
OL,18,Fwere Indian citizens - were told to
OL,19,Ffly into the UK on a temporary visitor
OL,20,Fvisa.
