OL,3,CFormer BA employee 'ran multi-million
OL,4,Cpound immigration scam from Heathrow'
OL,6,FThey would then book flights to Canada
OL,7,Fdespite not having a visa - as
OL,8,Frequired for Indian nationals who are
OL,9,Funable to enter Canada under the ETA
OL,10,F(Electronic Travel Authorisation)
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,FThe newspaper reported that at this
OL,14,Fstage, people would be directed to a
OL,15,Fcheck-in desk at Heathrow operated by
OL,16,Fthe alleged offender, who would
OL,17,Foverride the system and claim to have
OL,18,Fseen proof of an eligible visa.
