OL,3,CFormer BA employee 'ran multi-million
OL,4,Cpound immigration scam from Heathrow'
OL,6,FPolice suspect he ensured he was
OL,7,Frostered to be on the air-side team
OL,8,Fwho processed passengers at the
OL,9,Fboarding gate.
OL,11,FAfter making it into Canada,
OL,12,Fpassengers would immediately make an
OL,13,Fasylum claim.
OL,15,FThe scheme was reportedly discovered
OL,16,Fafter Canadian officials became
OL,17,Fsuspicious of a pattern that appeared
OL,18,Fto show passengers on BA flights to
OL,19,FToronto or Vancouver arriving without
OL,20,Fa visa to claim asylum.
