OL,3,CFormer BA employee 'ran multi-million
OL,4,Cpound immigration scam from Heathrow'
OL,6,FWhen police bailed the man last month,
OL,7,Fhe abandoned his life in the UK and
OL,8,Fflew to India with his partner, who
OL,9,Falso worked for BA.
OL,11,FBA said it has terminated the
OL,12,Femployment of both staff members.
OL,14,FPolice from both the UK and India -
OL,15,Fwhich share an extradition treaty -
OL,16,Fare now working in partnership to
OL,17,Ftrack down and arrest the unnamed pair.
OL,19,FIn a statement, BA said: "We are
OL,20,Fassisting the authorities with their
OL,21,Finvestigation."
